1.Importación de datos

params <- list(
  Fot12="Fot12",
  Fot34="Fot34",
  directorio= "/Users/estefaniagomezguil/Desktop/Fototipo12vs34Recod"
)
ruta_12<- file.path(params$directorio, "12")
ruta_34<- file.path(params$directorio, "34")

files_12 <- list.files(path = ruta_12, pattern = ".txt", full.names = TRUE)
files_34 <- list.files(path = ruta_34, pattern = ".txt", full.names = TRUE)
Grupo <- c (rep(params$Fot12, length(files_12)), rep(params$Fot34, length(files_34)))
